s as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointFeature":{"title":"MLNPointFeature","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointFeature","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointfeature","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointFeature","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object associates a point shape with an optional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"identifier and attributes."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointAnnotation":{"title":"MLNPointAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a one-dimensional shape located at a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single geographical coordinate. Depending on how it is used, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object is known as a point annotation or point shape. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point shape to represent a city at low zoom levels, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"address at high zoom levels, or the location of a long press gesture."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPointAnnotation"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointannotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointFeatureCluster":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointFeatureCluster"},{"type":"text","text":" object associates a point shape (with an optional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"identifier and attributes) and represents a point cluster."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointfeaturecluster","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPointFeatureCluster"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointFeatureCluster","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNPointFeatureCluster"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"title":"MLNShapeSource","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSource"}],"abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"text":" object along with an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"can update a shape source by setting its ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URL"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"title":"MLNAnnotationImage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNFeature":{"title":"MLNFeature","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnfeature","fragments":[{"text":"MLNFeature","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"  protocol is used to provide details about geographic features","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"contained in an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource"},{"type":"text","text":" object. Each concrete"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" in turn has a subclass that conforms to this protocol. A","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"feature object associates a shape with an optional identifier and attributes.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/GeoJSON":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/geojson","role":"article","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/GeoJSON","title":"Working with GeoJSON Data","kind":"article"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNVectorTileSource":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectortilesource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNVectorTileSource","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies tiled vector data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"text","text":"Mapbox Vector Tile"},{"type":"text","text":" format"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the tiles are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that conforms to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TileJSON specification"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A vector tile source is added to an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" objects. A vector style layer defines the appearance of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"any content supplied by the vector tile source."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNVectorTileSource","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"title":"MLNShape","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShape"}],"abstract":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content that forms the base map."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre"}}}